The word "Football" is also commonly used outside of the English-speaking world.

In Spanish-speaking countries the word has morphed into the Spanish phonetically-correct word "Fútbol" {{cite web|url=http://gl.wikipedia.org/wiki/F%C3%BAtbol|publisher=Wikipedia}}  to refer to Soccer Football.  In some instances the word "Fútbol" may be replaced by the word "Balonpié"  from the words "Balón" (ball) and "Pie" (foot).
